'''朵麗絲·阿貝利'''（Doris Abele），德國生物學家，擅長对[[南极|南极]]海洋生物的研究，在阿尔弗雷德·魏格纳研究所（AWI）领导研究团队对海洋无脊椎动物的胁迫生理及老化开展研究<ref name=":0"><cite class="citation web">tdeprez. </cite></ref>，并参与了“变化中地球系统的极地和海洋带生态”（PACES）项目。<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://epic.awi.de/view/awi_allPrograms/paces-2008-0202.html "Browse by Programs - ePIC"] {{Wayback|url=http://epic.awi.de/view/awi_allPrograms/paces-2008-0202.html |date=20210120164601 }}. ''epic.awi.de''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.awi.de/en/science/research-program.html "Research Program - AWI"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.awi.de/en/science/research-program.html |date=20210309174510 }}. ''www.awi.de''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>

== 早年生平及学历 ==
朵麗絲·阿貝利，1984毕业于[[杜塞尔多夫大学|杜塞尔多夫大学]]生物学专业，于1988年获得海洋生物学及生物化学博士学位，随后于1989年在[[不来梅大学|不来梅大学]]开展对氧自由基的博士后研究工作。<ref name=":1"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.embcplus.org/taxonomy/term/39481 "PD Dr. Doris Abele | EMBC+"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.embcplus.org/taxonomy/term/39481 |date=20190501012141 }}. ''www.embcplus.org''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>

== 学术成就及影响 ==
朵麗絲·阿貝利的研究领域包括外温动物的生理性衰老、基因和基因组的进化、气候变化对沿海底栖生物的影响，以及海洋有机体的HIF-1同系物。<ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.awi.de/ueber-uns/organisation/mitarbeiter/doris-abele.html "Dr. habil.] {{Wayback|url=https://www.awi.de/ueber-uns/organisation/mitarbeiter/doris-abele.html |date=20201025202423 }}</cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2015/11/151113181305.htm "Loss of diversity near melting coastal glaciers"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2015/11/151113181305.htm |date=20190501000622 }}. ''www.sciencedaily.com''. 2015-11-13<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref> 除科研论文外她也发表了大学教学材料<ref name=":0"><cite class="citation web">tdeprez. </cite></ref>和书籍。<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.expertsasia.eu/index.asp?p=262&a=260&mod=teacher&id=124 "Doris Abele"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.expertsasia.eu/index.asp?p=262&a=260&mod=teacher&id=124 |date=20190117174313 }}. ''expertsasia.eu''.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADoris+Abele&rft.atitle=Doris+Abele&rft.genre=unknown&rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.expertsasia.eu%2Findex.asp%3Fp%3D262%26a%3D260%26mod%3Dteacher%26id%3D124&rft.jtitle=expertsasia.eu&rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal" class="Z3988"> </span></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://au.wiley.com/WileyCDA/WileyTitle/productCd-1444335480.html "Oxidative Stress in Aquatic Ecosystems"]. </cite></ref>

自2007至2009，她协调了IPY_ClicOPEN项目「气候变化对南极半岛海岸带生态系统的影响」（Climate Change Effects on Coastal Ecosystems at the Antarctic Peninsula）。<ref name=":0"><cite class="citation web">tdeprez. </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">Abele, Doris (2007). </cite></ref><ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.predator.unsw.edu.au/page_1188265638812.html "Rogers Lab - University of New South Wales - ClicOPEN"] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20160831141458/http://www.predator.unsw.edu.au/page_1188265638812.html |date=2016-08-31 }}. ''www.predator.unsw.edu.au''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref name="#1"><cite class="citation web">tdeprez. </cite></ref> 自2011至2013年，她协调了IMCOAST项目“ 气候变化对南极海岸带生态系统的影响”。<ref name="esf.org"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.esf.org/hosting-experts/expert-boards-and-committees/polar-sciences/current-epb-initiatives/polarclimate.html "polarclimate : European Science Foundation"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.esf.org/hosting-experts/expert-boards-and-committees/polar-sciences/current-epb-initiatives/polarclimate.html |date=20160916102629 }}. ''www.esf.org''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref> 此外在2013-2016期间她担任了IMCONet跨学科西南极海岸带气候变化建模人员交流培训网络的协调员。<ref><cite class="citation web">[http://www.imconet.eu/about-the-project.html "About the Project"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.imconet.eu/about-the-project.html |date=20160914090428 }}. ''www.imconet.eu''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>

朵麗絲·阿貝利领导了9次在南极乔治国王岛Carlini科考站Dallmann实验室的科学考察， 以及国际ESF（欧洲社会基金）项目IMCOAST（气候变化对南极海岸带生态系统：2010-2016）。<ref name=":1"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.embcplus.org/taxonomy/term/39481 "PD Dr. Doris Abele | EMBC+"]. ''www.embcplus.org''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref name="esf.org"><cite class="citation web">[http://www.esf.org/hosting-experts/expert-boards-and-committees/polar-sciences/current-epb-initiatives/polarclimate.html "polarclimate : European Science Foundation"]. ''www.esf.org''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref><ref name="#1"/><ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.awi.de/nc/en/about-us/service/press/press-release/loss-of-diversity-near-melting-coastal-glaciers.html "Loss of Diversity Near Melting Coastal Glaciers - AWI"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.awi.de/nc/en/about-us/service/press/press-release/loss-of-diversity-near-melting-coastal-glaciers.html |date=20171116183053 }}. ''www.awi.de''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>在AWI就职期间她与{{link-en|英国南极调查局|British Antarctic Survey}}开展了广泛的合作。<ref><cite class="citation web">[https://www.bas.ac.uk/media-post/age-matters-to-antarctic-clams/ "PRESS RELEASE Age and Antarctic clams - News - British Antarctic Survey"] {{Wayback|url=https://www.bas.ac.uk/media-post/age-matters-to-antarctic-clams/ |date=20201118073209 }}. ''www.bas.ac.uk''<span class="reference-accessdate">. </span></cite></ref>此外她也在[[不来梅大学|不来梅大学]]从事教学工作。<ref name=":0"><cite class="citation web">tdeprez. </cite></ref>

